snippet.title: Release Date Announcement Trailer | Hob
snippet.description:
The world has waited thousands of years for you to explore, fix, save, and awake. The adventure begins, September 26, 2017. Hob: It's your chance. Make it home.

http://hobgame.com

Releasing September 26, 2017 on PlayStation, Steam, and GOG, for $19.99. Pre-orders begin August 1, 2017. See sites for more preorder bonuses, starting at 10% off. 

See the dynamic theme for Hob, here: 
https://youtu.be/a13crOAMkLM
Preorder now to transform your PS4 dashboard.


Connect with us!
